<template>
    <v-card>
        <v-list-item two-line>
            <v-list-item-content>
                <v-list-item-title>Przypisania Fibu</v-list-item-title>
                <v-list-item-subtitle>Znajdź lub aktualizuj bieżące przypisanie Fibu </v-list-item-subtitle>
            </v-list-item-content>
        </v-list-item>

        <v-divider></v-divider>

        <v-container>
            <v-card>
            <v-tabs
            color="deep-purple accent-4"
            right
            >
      <v-tab>Szukaj/Przypisz</v-tab>
      <v-tab>Zestawienie</v-tab>

      </v-tabs>
            <v-row>
                <v-col cols="3" class="d-column-flex ">
                    <v-autocomplete
                        dense
                        prepend-icon="mdi-magnify"
                        label="Nr FIBU">
                    </v-autocomplete>
                    <v-autocomplete
                        dense
                        prepend-icon="mdi-magnify"
                        label="Nazwa klienta">
                    </v-autocomplete>
                </v-col> 
                <v-col cols="5" class="d-column-flex ">
                    <v-autocomplete
                        dense
                        prepend-icon="mdi-magnify"
                        label="Nr FIBU">
                    </v-autocomplete>
                    <v-autocomplete
                        dense
                        prepend-icon="mdi-magnify"
                        label="Nazwa klienta">
                    </v-autocomplete>
                </v-col> 
                <v-col cols="4" class="d-column-flex ">
                    <v-autocomplete
                        dense
                        prepend-icon="mdi-magnify"
                        label="Nr FIBU">
                    </v-autocomplete>
                    <v-autocomplete
                        dense
                        prepend-icon="mdi-magnify"
                        label="Nazwa klienta">
                    </v-autocomplete>
                </v-col> 
            </v-row>    
            <v-card-actions>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
          <v-btn
          color="red darken-3"
            class="font-weight-regular"
            rounded
            outlined
            small
            @click="dialog = false"
          >
            Anuluj
          </v-btn>
          <v-btn
          color="green"
            class="font-weight-regular"
            rounded
            outlined
            small
            @click="dialog = false"
          >
            Zapisz
          </v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
    </v-card>
        </v-container>   
    </v-card>
</template>

<script>
import CardFibu from './Cards'
export default {

}
</script>

</style>
